                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00"/>
                           <desc>Fol.108vb: Donation note.</desc>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note is written in the main hand, rhymed. Zä-Wäldä Maryam is mentioned as the commissioner and donor.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- In some sections of a few miracles the word mǝʿǝraf "chapter" has been erased and replaced with a supplication note for the donor Zä-Wäldä Maryam written in fine small script: fols. 55va, 58ra, 59vb, 61vb, 62vb, 63va, 66va, 67va, 69rb, 81ra, 84va, 86vb, 92vb, 95ra, 105vb, 107ra. &#xD;
- Erased note: fol. 107va (several lines).&#xD;
- Crude, recent ownership note written in pen: fol. 108v. &#xD;
- Minor notes: fols. 8r and 26r (crossed out), 93v.&#xD;
- Drawings of crosses: fols. 3r, 12r.&#xD;
- Drawing of St. George, in pencil: fol. 1r.&#xD;
- Corrections written in the margins, in a fine small script: e.g., fols. 7rb, 8rb, 22vb, 27ra, 50vb, 80rb.&#xD;
- Erasures marked with parallel lines: e.g., fols. 3rb, 5rb, 9vb (several lines), 29va, 41vb.&#xD;
- Erasures without marking: fols. 13rab, 21ra, 25vb, 43va, 44rb.&#xD;
- Corrections over erased words or passages: fols. 5ra, 9vb, 19va, 29va, 34va, 41va,47vb, 73va, 80rb, 104ra, 105va. &#xD;
- Immediate corrections indicated by a line encircling the words: e.g., fols. 30vb, 86rab.&#xD;
- Pen trial: fol 2v.&#xD;
- Writing exercise: fols. 104v, 109v.&#xD;
- Crude doodles and letters, drawings by recent hands, in pen and pencil: e.g., fols. 77v, 78r, 89v.</item>
                     </list>
